    <h2>
        <a name="1"></a>How Do I...<br/>
        ...See A Doctor/Nurse?</h2>
    <p>
        When you register at the practice you will be given a copy of the practice booklet
        and an appointment will be made for a new registration check. You may consult with
        any doctor in the practice by making an appointment at reception either in person
        or by telephone. Every effort will be made to give you a convenient appointment
        with the doctor of your choice, but if this is not possible, then the receptionist
        will suggest an alternative.</p>
    <p>
        IF YOU ARE UNABLE TO KEEP YOUR APPOINTMENT, PLEASE INFORM US AS SOON AS POSSIBLE
        SO THAT ANOTHER PATIENT MAY BENEFIT FROM YOUR CANCELLATION - IF POSSIBLE PROVIDING
        24 HOURS' NOTICE.</p>
